thread.title: Victor & Siliva
thread.title_full: Nelson Alexander reviewed by Victor & Siliva

author: Victor & Siliva
title: Victor & Siliva
text: Our experience with Nelson Alexander was very positive. Peter and Celeste were open and honest which gave us confidence to move forward and put our trust with them in selling our property. Lines of communication were always open, and no question was too difficult. Although quite nervous on auction day, they both assured us they had the best outcome in mind. We were not disappointed. We would not hesitate in recommending Nelson Alexander, and in particular, Peter and Celeste (Preston office) to anyone.
